Package org.sopra.api

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BuildingConfig
    This interface provides building configuration parameters for play field element types.
    ConstructionCostCalculator
    This interface contains the functionality to calculate the costs to build a certain type of producer on a certain element on the playfield.
    CostCalculatorFactory
    Factory to create instances of cost calculators.
    EnergyNodeConfig
    This interface provides configuration parameters for energy nodes as described in the SoPra manual.
    Game
    A game contains the phases that are executed on a scenario.
    PowerLineConfig
    This interface models the design parameters for power lines/edges as described in the SoPra manual.
    Scenario
    A scenario is the data type the game is played on.
    Statistics
    The statistics contain several useful informations on the state of the scenario.
    UpgradePowerLineCostCalculator
    This interface contains the functionality to calculate the costs to upgrade the capacity of of power line.
